title: Protesters rally across America after Trump urges supporters to 'liberate' states
description: US President Donald Trump urges supporters to "liberate" three states held by Democratic governors, as hundreds of people gather outside government buildings to protest against stay-at-home restrictions aimed at stopping the coronavirus.
content:
Posted 
April 18, 2020 09:38:43
US President Donald Trump has urged supporters to "liberate" three states led by Democratic governors, apparently encouraging the growing protests against the stay-at-home restrictions aimed at stopping the coronavirus.
